# Complete Attack Reference Table

| Attack | Layer Hit | How Attacker Wins | Primary Defense |
|---|---|---|---|
| Stored XSS | Frontend | Inject persistent script via user content | DOMPurify + CSP |
| Reflected XSS | Frontend | Craft malicious URL → victim clicks | JSX rendering + input encoding |
| DOM XSS | Frontend | Manipulate DOM via URL hash/params | textContent over innerHTML |
| Mutation XSS | Frontend | Bypass sanitizers via browser parsing | DOMPurify (handles mXSS) |
| CSRF GET | Backend | Embed request in img tag | Never use GET for mutations |
| CSRF POST | Backend | Hidden auto-submitting form | CSRF tokens + SameSite cookie |
| CSRF JSON | Backend | Cross-origin fetch with credentials | SameSite=Strict + CORS |
| SQL Injection | Backend | Manipulate SQL query via input | Parameterized queries always |
| Union SQLi | Backend | UNION to dump other tables | Parameterized + least privilege |
| Blind SQLi | Backend | Infer data via true/false responses | Parameterized + no error leakage |
| Second-order SQLi | Backend | Stored payload used in later query | Parameterize ALL queries |
| Clickjacking | Frontend | Hidden iframe over your UI | X-Frame-Options: DENY + CSP |
| MITM | Network | Intercept HTTP traffic | HTTPS + HSTS + preload |
| SSL Stripping | Network | Downgrade HTTPS to HTTP | HSTS with preload |
| Credential Stuffing | Auth | Leaked passwords from other breaches | Rate limit + MFA + HaveIBeenPwned |
| Brute Force | Auth | Try all password combinations | Rate limit + bcrypt cost 12+ |
| Session Fixation | Auth | Pre-set known session ID | Regenerate session after login |
| Data Exposure | API | Over-fetching or logged secrets | Select only needed fields |
| Open Redirect | Frontend | Redirect to phishing site | Whitelist redirect destinations |
| Prototype Pollution | Backend | Pollute Object.prototype via JSON | freeze prototype + validate keys |
| Insecure Deserialize | Backend | Craft malicious serialized payload | JWT + schema validation |
| Subdomain Takeover | DNS/Infra | Claim dangling CNAME target | Audit DNS + delete before decommission |
| Supply Chain | CI/Build | Malicious npm package | npm audit + lock versions + Socket.dev |

